The number of swap matrices with 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

 rows, 
\begin_inset Formula $n>1$
\end_inset

, is 
\begin_inset Formula ${\displaystyle \frac{n(n-1)}{2}}$
\end_inset

