\begin_layout Enumerate
If 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 are identical except in their 
\begin_inset Formula $k^{th}$
\end_inset

 columns where 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{:,k}=cB_{:,k}$
\end_inset

, then 
